Subject: Re: Endless loop in Halo 1.06


I heard you can create a loop by using "BASEIC" code by going into the
menu running

10 Click on "Settings" 
20 Click on "Main Menu" 
30 Click on "Settings" 
40 Click on "Main Menu" 
50 GOTO 10


